    dc:description "PLATE 85. A, C. Heads of Female. B. Pronotum, lateral view. D–F. Chelae. A, B, D. Dryinus stantoni, female from Sabah (from Olmi 1984). C, E. D. trifasciatus, female from Laos (from Olmi 1984). F. D. anotaulicus, holotype (from Xu et al. 2011f). Scale bar 1.95 mm for A, 1.27 mm for B, 1.34 mm for C, 0.35 mm for D, 0.30 mm for E and 0.20 mm for F." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5278676/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

